items.title: Enzyme's worth to biofuels shown in recent research
items.summary: A newly discovered enzyme proves adept at breaking down cellulose fibers regardless of whether their crystalline structure is simple or highly complex. No other enzyme has shown that ability.

alternate.title: Enzyme's worth to biofuels shown in recent research

items.title: Beta blockers not needed after heart attack if other medications taken
items.summary: Beta blockers are not needed after a heart attack if heart-attack survivors are taking ACE inhibitors and statins, new research suggests. The study is the first to challenge the current clinical guideline that heart-attack survivors should take all three drugs -- beta blockers, ACE inhibitors and statins -- for the rest of their lives.

alternate.title: Beta blockers not needed after heart attack if other medications taken

items.title: Sex, aggression controlled separately in female animal brains, but overlap in male brains
items.summary: Brain structures that control sexual and aggressive behavior in mice are wired differently in females than in males, new research shows.
